                                                </p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <a
                                            href={downloadUrl}
                                            target="_blank"
                                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                            class="w-full md:w-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 border border-transparent text-lg font-bold rounded-xl shadow-xl text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500 transition-all duration-300"
                                            download={fileName}
                                        >
                                            📥 Unduh Sekarang
                                        </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>}

                                <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
                                    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-3">
                                        Panduan Pengunduhan
                                    </h3>
                                    <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-2">
                                        <li class="flex items-start">
                                            <svg
                                                class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
                                                fill="none"
                                                stroke="currentColor"
                                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                            >
                                                <path
                                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                                    stroke-width="2"
                                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                                                />
                                            </svg>
                                            <span>
                                                Klik tombol "Unduh Sekarang"
                                                untuk mengunduh file
                                            </span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="flex items-start">
                                            <svg
                                                class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
                                                fill="none"
                                                stroke="currentColor"
                                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                            >
                                                <path
                                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                                    stroke-width="2"
                                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                                                />
                                            </svg>
                                            <span>
                                                File akan otomatis terunduh ke
                                                perangkat Anda
                                            </span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="flex items-start">
                                            <svg
                                                class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
                                                fill="none"
                                                stroke="currentColor"
                                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                            >
                                                <path
                                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                                    stroke-width="2"
                                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                                                />
                                            </svg>
                                            <span>
                                                Tautan ini hanya berlaku untuk 7
                                                hari sejak pembelian
                                            </span>
                                        </li>
                                        <li class="flex items-start">
                                            <svg
                                                class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-500 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
                                                fill="none"
                                                stroke="currentColor"
                                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                            >
                                                <path
                                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                                    stroke-width="2"
                                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                                                />
                                            </svg>
                                            <span>
                                                Hanya dapat diakses dengan
                                                email:{" "}
